  "description": "This image presents a dramatic and captivating scene of a sunset or sunrise as seen through the silhouette of mountainous terrain. The sun is obscured by the peaks, but its intense glow creates a vibrant burst of light just behind the mountains. This light bleeds upward, painting the sky in shades of fiery orange and red, contrasted against a darkening sky. The mountain range itself is completely black, emphasizing its strong and jagged outline against the illuminated backdrop. The overall effect is one of immense scale and natural beauty, evoking a sense of awe and wonder.",
